subsection.def:
Register of Escalator
                    Contractors (自動梯承辦商名冊) means the
                register established and kept under section 105(1)(b);

Register of Escalator Engineers
                    (自動梯工程師名冊) means the register established and
                kept under section 105(1)(d);

registered escalator contractor
                    (註冊自動梯承辦商) means a person who is registered
                under section 86 and whose registration is in force;

registered escalator engineer
                    (註冊自動梯工程師) means a person who is registered
                under section 90 and whose registration is in force;

